{"word":"ὑγιαίνω","slug":"ὑγιαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑγιαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑγιής\">ὑγιής</a></el>] ‘be in a state of well-being’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on physical condition <b>be well <a href='B:490 5:31'>Lk 5:31</a>; <a href='B:490 7:10'>7:10</a>; <a href='B:490 15:27'>15:27</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 2</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on non-physical condition <b>be wholesome/sound:</b> of instruction (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διδασκαλία\">διδασκαλία</a></el>) <b><a href='B:610 1:10'>1 Ti 1:10</a>; <a href='B:620 4:3'>2 Ti 4:3</a>; <a href='B:630 1:9'>Tit 1:9</a>; <a href='B:630 2:1'>2:1</a>;</b> of verbal presentation (<el>λόγοι</el>) <b><a href='B:610 6:3'>1 Ti 6:3</a>; <a href='B:620 1:13'>2 Ti 1:13</a>;</b> of loyalty or commitment (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πίστις\">πίστις</a></el>) <b><a href='B:630 1:13'>Tit 1:13</a>; <a href='B:630 2:2'>2:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑβριστής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑγιής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}